{"TopicId":187383,"ForumId":109,"TopicTitle":"Will there be pre-order available?","CreatedByName":"jwanders","CreatedById":199559,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-20T06:10:10Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"jwanders","CreatedById":199559,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-20T06:10:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWill it be possible to pre-order the new version? Also, will the 2.x version follow a similar upgrade path as the 1.x did? (Started playing in the 0.9x phase).....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CCCircuit","CreatedById":201622,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-30T01:44:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen can we preorder?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"mcwaffles2003","CreatedById":180102,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-30T04:14:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223654198\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187383\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566281410\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022199559\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022jwanders\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 8/20/2019 at 2:10 AM, jwanders said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWill it be possible to pre-order the new version? Also, will the 2.x version follow a similar upgrade path as the 1.x did? (Started playing in the 0.9x phase).....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwell hopefully theyll be starting from at least an improved 1.5\u00A0as production began before the 1.6\u00A0update as evidenced by the model for the poodle engine\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-30T04:32:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat benefits, other than avoiding forgetting it exists and therefore never buying it or playing it totally by accident, do you expect a pre-order to grant you?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MechBFP","CreatedById":184845,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-30T12:57:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223711523\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187383\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221575088375\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002273725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u00225thHorseman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 hours ago, 5thHorseman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat benefits, other than avoiding forgetting it exists and therefore never buying it or playing it totally by accident, do you expect a pre-order to grant you?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy preorder bonuses of course!\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbart","CreatedById":78303,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-30T13:37:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223711523\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187383\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221575088375\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002273725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u00225thHorseman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 hours ago, 5thHorseman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat benefits, other than avoiding forgetting it exists and therefore never buying it or playing it totally by accident, do you expect a pre-order to grant you?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEntitlement to unlimited upgrades and DLC, and the moral right to complain about it when DLC is only available after paying for it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223654198\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187383\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566281410\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022199559\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022jwanders\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 8/20/2019 at 2:10 AM, jwanders said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, will the 2.x version follow a similar upgrade path as the 1.x did? (Started playing in the 0.9x phase).....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m going to assume Star \u003Cs\u003EHelix \u003C/s\u003ETheory learned from Squad\u0027s mistakes and will \u003Cem\u003Enot\u003C/em\u003E follow that ill-fated path. Rushing through beta (to make certain -I guess- financial deadlines) was proven to be a very bad idea, given the bugfest the early 1.0 releases were.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-11-30T13:39:57Z\u0022 title=\u002211/30/2019 01:39  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003ENovember 30, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Kerbart\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-30T15:35:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf invest the preorder money in some proper stock instead of preordering, and wait till the coming spring, maybe the received interest will be enough for a Kerbal T-shirt.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nP.S.\u003Cbr\u003E\nOr a Kerbal hand watch. With six hours in a day.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-11-30T15:35:48Z\u0022 title=\u002211/30/2019 03:35  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003ENovember 30, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by kerbiloid\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xd the great","CreatedById":188222,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-12-01T08:44:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223711663\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187383\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221575128132\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 hours ago, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nP.S.\u003Cbr\u003E\nOr a Kerbal hand watch. With six hours in a day.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat will do.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nP.S. will KSP 2 days be longer or shorter?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"dave1904","CreatedById":153882,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-12-17T21:40:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy? its not like steam is going to run out of copies on day one.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"mcwaffles2003","CreatedById":180102,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-12-17T21:50:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223712009\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187383\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221575189853\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022188222\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Xd the great\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 12/1/2019 at 3:44 AM, Xd the great said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022#\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/a\u003E \u003Cspan\u003EHide contents\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nP.S. will KSP 2 days be longer or shorter?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey said they were keeping the Kerbol system the same so I\u0027d assume they\u0027ll still be about 6 hours long\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"mattinoz","CreatedById":118580,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-12-18T07:32:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223654198\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187383\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566281410\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022199559\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022jwanders\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 8/20/2019 at 4:10 PM, jwanders said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, will the 2.x version follow a similar upgrade path as the 1.x did?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nReally doubt it. Commercial developer that has accounting standards to meet.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere will be most likely some regular DLC to fund ongoing development.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"derbleifuss","CreatedById":200103,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-12-18T15:41:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223718443\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187383\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221576619453\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022180102\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022mcwaffles2003\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 hours ago, mcwaffles2003 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey said they were keeping the Kerbol system the same so I\u0027d assume they\u0027ll still be about 6 hours long\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut let\u0027s hope they finally add the Gas Planet 2 beyond Jool\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-12-18T15:52:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223718656\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187383\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221576683669\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022200103\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022derbleifuss\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 minutes ago, derbleifuss said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut let\u0027s hope they finally add the Gas Planet 2 beyond Jool\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy, when they could add Gas Planets 2 through N to the other stars?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DRAG0Nmon","CreatedById":196609,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-12-21T01:59:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI hope they have some early-access program, I would so do that!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}